Subject: [PATCH] Reduce theme-compiler.js to single public export

- Remove re-export of slugToTitle (already in slug-utils.js)
- Unexport extractRootVariables and getThemeFiles (internal helpers)
- Move slugToTitle tests to slug-utils.test.js where it belongs
- Simplify theme-compiler.test.js to only test generateThemeSwitcherContent
- Remove 3 entries from ALLOWED_TEST_ONLY_EXPORTS

This addresses the code smell where we were exporting internal implementation
details solely for testing. Tests now verify the public API output works
correctly rather than testing implementation internals.
